Our discussions with LIMITrader had been halted as they were unable to

provide a contact for legal and operational issues.  However, Mike Lanier

(mlanier@limitrader.com / 212-499-1390) indicated today that he will

coordinate responding to any Enron issues.


Paul, please respond to Sara  and Jason as to whether you would like

discussions with LIMITrader to resume.  LIMITrader supports online trading of

high yield and broken convertibles.  Investment grade is expected to be added

in late January.


Thanks.


Mike


